{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, there are 266 different domains which only have one associated fact-check.",
    "Figure 4 shows the total amount of fact-checks in the dataset per month.",
    "While the oldest fact-check in the dataset was published in 2011, we see that very few fact-checks were uploaded until early 2019.",
    "Since then the dataset contains a relatively stable amount of around eight hundred fact-checks per month.",
    "To use the Data Commons dataset we need to standardize the dataset."
  ]
}